ass=\"slide-container\" id=\"analyse\">\n                            <div class=\"slide-image\">\n                                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-6-2.png\" alt=\"toovalu-impact-logiciel-analyse-diagramme\" aria-label=\"toovalu-impact-logiciel-analyse-diagramme\">\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"carousel-controls\">\n                                <label for=\"img-2\" class=\"prev-slide\">\n                                    <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow-1.png\" <=\"\" span=\"\">\n                                </span></label>\n                                <label for=\"img-1\" class=\"next-slide\">\n                                    <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\"></span>\n                                </label>\n                            </div>\n                        </li>\n                        <div class=\"carousel-dots\">\n                            <label for=\"img-1\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-1\"></label>\n                            <label for=\"img-2\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-2\"></label>\n                            <label for=\"img-3\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-3\"></label>\n                        </div>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-space-around pb-4\">\n                <a href=\"/contact/\" class=\"btn btn--blue\">watch the demo</a>\n                <a href=\"/solutions/\" class=\"btn btn--pink\">Discover more about our solutions</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid2 pb-2\">\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell alignItemCenter\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1536-1024.jpeg\" alt=\"equipe-toovalu\" aria-label=\"equipe-toovalu\">\n        </div>\n        <div>\n            <h2 class=\"text-center pt-0\">the Toovalu <em>Touch !</em></h2>\n            <p class=\"mr-3 ml-3\"><strong>Technology</strong> proposing a management of the company by the impact by plunging to the roots of your data to make them useful! And thus helping the leaders and decision-markers to integrate CSR, climate issues and their impacts at the heart of their strategy.<br>\nWith now 10 years of experience, we know how to go to the point and target your needs to save you time and act concretely on the climate and CSR.\n                We have developed an approach both agile and respecting the philosophy of th Carbon® balance.\n                With TOOVALU, climate & CSR integrate your strategy and become useful\n                and illuminating steering tools.\n\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-center pt-2 pb-2\"><a href=\"/a-propos-de-nous\" class=\"btn\">À propos de nous</a></p>\n            <div class=\"grid4 grid4-sm grid2-xs\">\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Pilot</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-79.png\" alt=\"toovalu-seminar\" aria-label=\"toovalu-seminaire\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Enforce</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-89.png\" alt=\"toovalu-report-bicycle\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Communicate</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-95.png\" alt=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\" aria-label=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>To hire</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-98.png\" alt=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid4 grid2-sm\">\n        <div class=\"bg-blue\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-center ff-light\">A </span><span> carbon footprint</span>\n            <p class=\"text-center ff-light\">that sees far</p>\n        </h3></div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_BC-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-seminar\" aria-label=\"toovalu-seminaire\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-pink\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-center ff-light\">Construct your</span><br>\n                <span>PATH</span>\n                <br>low-carbon</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Trajectoire.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Piloter-copie-retouch.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\" aria-label=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-yellow\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span>Pilot</span><br> <span> YOUR STRATEGIES</span><br>\n                <span class=\"text-center ff-light\">in complete serenity!</span>\n            </h3><br>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Construction.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-Team-bike\" aria-label=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-green\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\">\n                <span class=\"ff-light\">A tool</span><br>\n                <span>COLLABORATIVE <br>\n                            <span>&amp;</span>\n                            <br>\n                        <span>and committed</span>\n                        </span>\n            </h3>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"content content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-columns mb-0\">\n                <div class=\"wp-block-column flex-align-items\">\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/BCORP_logo.png\" alt=\"b-corp\" aria-label=\"b-corp-logo\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis: 66%;\">\n                    <h3 class=\"mt-0\">Take part in the business movement with positive impact !!\n                    </h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-center \">TOOVALU has become BCORP in 2017, one of the first in Nantes. With <a class=\"color-green pink-visited\" href=\"https://www.bcorporation.fr\">B-corp</a>\n                        , we aim to demonstrate our positive impact on society, and we agree to be evaluated on our overall performance every two years</p>\n                    <p class=\"pt-2 bt-2\"><a href=\"/a-propos-de-nous\" class=\"btn\">En savoir +</a></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"testimonial\">\n        <h2 class=\"color-blue text-center\">\n            <em>They witness</em>\n        </h2>\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-1\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-2\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-3\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-4\">\n        <ul class=\"slides\">\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>The meeting between the methodological expertise and the features of the TOOVALU tool creates the synergy needed to support our group in reducing its impacts.</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">SYSTEME U<br>\n                                Jean-Michel GUILLOU responsable pôle QSSE Produits Fournisseurs\n                                </span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>A reliable, traceable, simple, clear, effective tool</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">BNP PARIBAS REAL ESTATE </span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>At Toovalu, the proposed formulas allow each company to succeed in its DEF regardless of its degree of maturity. </q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">SFPI <br>\n                                Sophie Morel, Juriste et Administratrice Groupe</span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>The TOOVALU tool transforms the DPEF constraint into a real pilotage opportunity. With TOOVALU, we went from a centralized indicator collection to a business-oriented steering. Everyone has appropriated the platform and integrates it fully in its reporting</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">HERIGE<br>\n                                Caroline Lutinier CSR Manager</span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slidesNavigation\">\n            <label for=\"radio-1\" id=\"dotForRadio-1\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-2\" id=\"dotForRadio-2\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-3\" id=\"dotForRadio-3\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-4\" id=\"dotForRadio-4\"></label>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- #main -->\n    <!-- #primary -->\n<!-- /wp:html -->','home en','','publish','closed','closed','','home-en','','','2021-10-28 15:28:28','2021-10-28 15:28:28','',0,'http://testsite2.local/home-fr-english/',0,'page','',0);
